{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_03_02",
  "title": "奥山すみれ 2話 やっと見せた笑顔",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "奥山さんを怒らせてしまったぞ……早く探さないと\nあっいた、奥山さん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I made Okuyama angry… I have to find her quickly.\nThere you are‚ Okuyama!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 6.1666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "話し掛けないで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t talk to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "頼むから機嫌を直して俺の話を聞いてくれないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m begging you‚ calm down and listen to what I have to say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "いーっだ\nこれから仕事なので失礼します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ne—ver.\nI have work to do‚ so please excuse me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2366.666666700002,
          "startTime": 19.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "取り付く島もないな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t get through to you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "むー……\nどこまでついて来るんですか。ストーカーですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmph…\nHow long are you going to keep following me? Are you a stalker?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーなんだから\n仕事について行くに決まってるだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m a manager‚\nof course I’m going with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それより次の仕事まで時間があるから\nどこかで食事でもしながら話さないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And we have time before the next job‚\nso why don’t we go and get a meal somewhere?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "今日は瑠依ちゃんや優ちゃんと一緒に\nご飯を食べるのでいりません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today I’ll be eating with Rui and Yu‚\nso no thanks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "……本当ならクリスマスイブも\n三人でケーキを食べるはずだったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The three of us should have been\neating cake together on Christmas Eve.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん達に食べてほしくて\nクリスマスケーキを作る練習までしたんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I even learned to make Christmas cake‚\nI even practiced baking Christmas cake.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "子役をしていた頃からクリスマスはいつもお仕事で\nお友達とパーティーなんてしたことなかったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since I was a child actress‚ Christmas Even has always been about work‚\nand I’ve never had a party with friends‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんや優ちゃんと過ごすクリスマスイブを\nすっごく楽しみにしてたのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so I was really looking forward to enjoying Christmas Eve\ntogether with Rui and Yu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "謝っても許してあげません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won’t forgive you just because you say sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "なぁ、何か温かいものでも飲まないか？\nそこの自販機で飲み物を買うけど奥山さんは何がいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ how about we get a hot drink?\nI’m getting a drink from that vending machine. Okuyama‚ what would you like?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "話し掛けないで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t talk to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、俺はこのおしるこにしようかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ I’ll have the red bean soup.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "あ、それは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ that’s…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "前に奥山さんにオススメされたことがあっただろ？\nあれ以来、たまに無性に飲みたくなるんだよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s what you recommended to me before‚ right?\nSince then‚ I sometimes get an urge to drink it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "その気持ち分かります！\n寒い日はおしるこを飲みたくなりますよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know how you feel!\nCold days make me want to drink red bean soup.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "あ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "奥山さんの分も買おうか？\n少しでもお詫びしたいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Should I get you one too‚ Okuyama?\nAs a little apology…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_02-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですね\nおごってくれるなら飲んであげてもいいです",
